author: Justin Hoyo
text:
Outlet was smaller than I expected, but rather cozy! Dumbbells so up to 40kg, and there were sufficient number of weight plates. The gym was super neat, cleaned, and well-maintained.

Staff here were friendly and helpful. Members can also use the evolt body scanner for free (take note only during staffed hours).

In terms of locations, it‚Äôs near the park, but not very convenient to get to, and no shopping malls nearby. But a good thing is that it‚Äôs more quiet and less crowded than other gyms.

author: Emily Tee
text:
Absolutely love this neighborhood gym! It‚Äôs got a cozy, welcoming vibe that makes working out feel way more enjoyable. The space is always clean and well-maintained!
What really makes it stand out is the team of staff. Everyone I've met is friendly and approachable!
Highly recommend if you‚Äôre looking for a gym that feels like part of the community.

author: M Ang
text:
Small and cosy Anytime Fitness tucked at a corner in Waterway. Being located right next to a park it feels zen to be working out here. Although the space is small it's quite well utilized and there's a variety of equipments. Space is clean and the weights are tidily placed unlike most of the other outlets where you can't find the plates at the destinated rack.
Free for members to use evolt360 during staffed hours is a bonus.

author: Kash ‚ÄúAngler Kash‚Äù Hyqal
text:
One of the best gyms I‚Äôve been to! The place is always clean, well-maintained, and equipped with everything you need. Free weights to machines that are in top-notch condition. You can tell the management really takes pride in keeping the equipment and facilities in great shape.

But what really makes this gym stand out is the staff. They‚Äôre friendly, approachable, and always ready to help, whether it‚Äôs asking about nutrition or giving small tips to improve form. You don‚Äôt often see this level of attentiveness and professionalism in many gyms. A welcoming and motivating environment that makes you actually look forward to coming in.

Overall, it‚Äôs not just a place to train, it‚Äôs a place where you feel supported and encouraged to push your limits safely. Highly recommend! üí™

author: Guo hong
text:
The gym is always clean, well-maintained, and equipped with everything I need, from cardio machines to free weights and functional training gear.
What really sets this place apart is the staffs. The staffs are approachable, knowledgeable, and genuinely care about helping members reach their goals.

author: Elson Sim
text:
I‚Äôve been quite impressed with my experience at Anytime Fitness Waterway. The gym is always clean, well-maintained, and equipped with everything you need for a good workout.

A special shout-out to Pauline and Delvyn. They make the place stands out. Pauline is always welcoming and attentive, creating such a positive and motivating atmosphere the moment you walk in. Delvyn is knowledgeable and genuinely passionate about fitness, he goes the extra mile to guide and encourage members, whether you‚Äôre just starting out or working on specific goals.

Their friendliness and professionalism make every visit a great experience. Definitely one of the best Anytime Fitness branches I‚Äôve been to.

author: Jordan Chong
text: What I like is there are some unique training possibilities with new equipment (in pic1). The gym still have room for least 5 equipments, so hopefully they are able to add based on demand. I was excited to see EVOLT body scanner but I was disappointed that was intentionally locked from self-service usage. I am doubtful of the intent of the gym owner. What's the point if you have equipment but not letting users to use it. For additional income?

author: N H
text: Though modest in size, this outlet offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The coaches and fitness instructors are approachable, knowledgeable, and always willing to assist, regardless of whether you‚Äôve enrolled in one-on-one coaching. The equipment is well maintained, making this an excellent place for both a quality workout and reliable fitness guidance.

author: Zulkiflee Mohamad
text: AF Punggol Waterway's PTs are friendly. The place is clean & neat. Always smell pleasant despite the overload of different aromas. Good vibes and the best way to start or end your day :)

author: Shameel Tang
text: Fantastic location and brand new equipment. Combining traditional bodybuilding equipment with functional training equipment like SkiErg and sled pulls as well.

author: Felix Ko
text: Great gym with a nice view! Lovely staff, well equipped, always kept clean and conveniently located!

author: freddy zachary
text: I am delighted to be the inaugural member to utilize the facilities at Anytime Fitness Waterway Sunrise on its launch day, and I must say that the experience has exceeded my expectations. Although the space may be compact, the ambiance is genuinely motivational and conducive to a productive workout. The state-of-the-art equipment is not only brand new but also of the highest quality, ensuring a safe and effective exercise experience. The staff's warm hospitality and friendly demeanor create a welcoming atmosphere for everyone, fostering a sense of community among members. Given its proximity to my residence, I am enthusiastic about incorporating this gym into my regular fitness routine, which I anticipate will yield significant benefits. Overall, I am thoroughly impressed and motivated to achieve new heights in my fitness journey.

author: Muhammad muizzuddeen
text: Gym is well equipped even though it is slightly smaller than average. Staff were very warm and welcoming to members, especially brand ambassador, Shahmi, who helped me ensure a smooth and pleasant sign up :) 10/10 playlist in the gym too!!

author: Shawa Property
text: I am totally new to gym and had no past experiences at all. Chanced upon this outlet and was won over by the warm hospitality and passion of the staffs. Bite the bullet, signed up and totally never regret it! Though it is of a smaller outlet as compare to a lot more branches, the machines and equipments were considered relatively decent. Kudos to Valerie, Delvyn & Shahmi for being super helpful and friendly and always assisting me whenever I needed help! üëçüèº

author: XI EN TOH
text:
i have many good things to say about af waterway!
firstly the staff is super welcoming to everyone who steps in the gym and make them feel comfortable! especially shahmi! he super helpful and loves to give little tips to people who struggle with their form in their exercises! giving them 5 stars is an understatement, they should be deserving more stars given that their service and attitude towards everyday work. super grateful to be signing my membership with them and i hope they get their flowers for the unwavering dedication they put in their everyday work!

author: Isaac Nathan
text: Great experience training at this outlet. It‚Äôs usually quiet, which makes for a focused and stress-free workout. The environment is clean, lighting is great, and the equipments are new and well-chosen for the space. Perfect spot if you prefer training without the crowd.

author: Denzel
text:
I would like to sincerely recommend Valerie to anyone seeking a dedicated and effective Personal Trainer. Having known her for several years, I‚Äôve witnessed her remarkable personal transformation, an inspiring journey that led me to engage her as my own trainer.

Over the course of our sessions, Valerie provided constructive feedback and guidance that played a significant role in helping me become leaner, stronger, and fitter. She approaches each session with patience and brings with her a wealth of knowledge in both fitness and nutrition, which greatly accelerated my progress toward my goals.

If you‚Äôre looking for a Personal Trainer with a proven track record and a genuine commitment to her clients' success, I highly recommend reaching out to Valerie.

author: Paul Young
text:
Brand new location with brand new equipment and brand new smell. Great place to workout after a long day at work.

I followed the PT Trainer Valerie from her previous post at AF SKH, because under her guidance and regime, my percentage body fat went from 16.8% to 12.8%. Would highly recommend her coaching services to anyone who wants to achieve their fitness goals.

author: David Aljecera
text: Wonderful gym with wonderful staff! Coach Valerie is very good at teaching and has workout plans for any person with a goal in mind. I highly recommend her as your personal trainer as I myself lost 4kgs in 3 months under her excellent care.

author: Aaron Yin
text: Gym is not as big as the nearby gyms, but have exactly what you need to get a good workout in! Staff are all very friendly as well. 100% will recommend for you to get a workout in

author: Justin Tan
text: New, nice and cozy gym perfect for those who live around here. Signages placed around the gym to remind members to keep the place neat. Toilet is also kept clean.

author: Benjamin
text: I like this outlet, friendly crew, good place to get your workouts done. Hygiene wise is great too, every morning I seen janitors coming in to ensure equipments are cleaned.

author: Owen
text: Delvyn is really helpful and approachable whenever we ask for guidance. He gave us useful tips on how to do our workouts correctly and advised us on which exercises to focus on based on our goals. Great experience at Anytime Fitness Waterway:)

author: Jensen Mah
text: Love this new AF gym to workout in! Space is cozy and well equipped to train in! The team is friendly and welcoming too! Great Experience!

text:

text:

Like a small community gym with 3 treadmills, 1 row, 1 bike, 2 power racks, 1 smith, 1 leg press/curl/ex, 1 cable machines, dumbbell max 40kg, 3 benches, 1 pulley, 1 ski cardio, 1 machine fly, 1 chest press, 1 shoulder press, 1 vertical row‚Ä¶

No space for moving the bench.. 7-8 max
